TomGine Render Engine
API: tgEngine.h, tgTomGineThread.h

OpenGL Rendering engine for displaying 3D objects.

Modules:
    - Rendering engine [tgTomGineThread, tgTomGineThreadPCL, tgEngine]
    - Collission detection (Ray-Triangle, Ray-Model intersection tests) [tgCollission]
    - Capture point-cloud from virtual scene [tgEngine]
    - Error metric for different objectes [tgErrorMetric]
    - View frustum calculations [tgFrustum]
    - PLY model loader [tgModelLoader]
    - 2D oszilloscope-like plotting [tgPlot2D]
    - Quaternions [tgQuaternion]
    - Creating basic shapes (box, sphere, cylinders, planes, ...) [tgShapeCreator]

Requirements
	rt		(real-time clock)
	freeglut3-dev
    libglew1.6-dev
    X11, X11-xcb
	libftgl2, libftgl-dev (render text in OpenGL)
	libhighgui-dev (opencv - image file loading/saving)
	
Keyboard mapping:
	[Escape]: Close programme
	[w]: Toggle wireframe mode
	[Keypad_0, z]:	Reset to initial camera view
	
Mouse mapping:
	[Left Mouse Button + Move]: Rotate view about COR (Center of Rotation)
	[Right Mouse Button + Move]: Translate view
	[Mouse Wheel]: Zoom in/out

